channel.title: Pi Webclient Cache Problem
channel.description: Hey i made an webclient got everything working it downloads webclient and extracts but it dosent use the one i uploaded.... :confused: I uploaded mine to drop box and added the links to cache downloaded and client.java and it still uses the old sprites that i dont want... Please help!

item.title: Pi Webclient Cache Problem
item.dc:creator: @ExtremeX-Scape Ryley
item.description:
@ExtremeX-Scape wrote:

You either
A. Uploaded wrong cache
B. didn’t change the cache name and it’s loading from the old cache in you’re C:/
C. You didn’t update you’re sprites like you thought you did.
